lines.text: You know it could take us weeks to find where this thing is holed up. I mean it could be in the woods. Away from the city someplace, could be over in Jersey some place. My God with a wingspan like you're talking about here, that thing could fly miles into New York every day. And it would do that of course, you know because, New York is famous for good eating
Stick it in your brain. Your tiny little brain!
I am the plumed serpent, I fly, and I crawl... I have fallen, but I shall rise again!
